				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1350">Black Burrow</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Stackable Gnoll Pelts</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Stackable Gnoll Pelts</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=425214"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:jamieg@neo.rr.com">Jamie Gellner</a> | 
		                        5/9/2001 5:21:58 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Collect about 64-128 stackable gnoll pelts from Black Burrow and get a large sowing kit.  Combine 4 pelts, you will get a patch.  Make 4 patches.  Combine those 4 patches and you will get something new, i think it's called a square.  Make 4 squares, combine them and you will get a cloak I think (I havn't finished the quest).  Give it to Cappi McTarnigal in the rogue guild, he should give you one of the best piercing weapons in the game!!!
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
